{"tid":1203452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實所謂兄弟爬山 各有各做只係無奈之舉","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T10:41:28.000Z","uid":137220,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d980560d6e99bbbcadafb7d5cd71f9f521fbb6b5","tid":1203452,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"作為一個個人選擇，你有你苦衷，你唔出黎，或者和平散去無人怪到你<br />\n<br />\n但當暴政存在，推翻佢就係所有人嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n根本所有人都心知肚明， 正確做法得一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以話， 我做唔到100分，做50分你都冇必要鬧我呀？ <br />\n<br />\n而事實就係，你要推返呢條法例，甚至推翻呢個政府只係得&quot;得&quot;同埋&quot;唔得&quot; 呢兩樣選擇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你係一個有影響力嘅人, 你叫人和平散去, 和理非非, 而阻止人哋去做更激烈嘅抗爭<br />\n可以好肯定咁講，你係錯，絕對值得人哋去批判你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係而家呢個時勢，所謂兄弟爬山各有各做，只係唔想內鬥， 好似以前有段時間國民黨同共產黨合作抗戰咁， 只希望班人唔好好似共產黨咁， 一路拖後腳"},{"pid":"64a6f8c2aa3303a45315716a2003c7d00b5467b7","tid":1203452,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7dc40c770ec1011c2433ee4bb998fff79f9b87e","tid":1203452,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469c15fe45af94be7cd985879b727e986a0b09d2","tid":1203452,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fba8f72059de7c921160290dd0d0f5fa62084f","tid":1203452,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1a10eff878bf1fa56ad5b641fee0ee0d3cb1f9","tid":1203452,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif